CNCP v1 23035
{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#9296: `defineComponent` behaves differently in js and ts",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:23:34.724253+00:00",
  "text": "`defineComponent` behaves differently in js and ts\n\n### Vue version\n\n3.3.4\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\n\nhttps://play.vuejs.org/#\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nJust checkout `a.ts` and `b.js`, then trigger autocomplete.\n\n### What is expected?\n\n![image](https://github.com/vuejs/core/assets/58381667/78bf6f75-9e21-44a7-a589-f1b9fb6d7c45)\n\n### What is actually happening?\n\n![image](https://github.com/vuejs/core/assets/58381667/3fd7b0e4-1ec9-482e-98bc-a26b870b842d)\r\n\n\n### System Info\n\n_No response_\n\n### Any additional comments?\n\n_No response_",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    "scope: types",
    ":cake: p2-nice-to-have"
  ],
